Prerequisite:
Install Eclipse, Android SDK and NDK
This project should be placed under samples in the NDK install dir

Update ant buildfiles
android update project -p . -s
i.e.: /Users/bc/android-sdk-macosx/tools/android update project -p . -s

Build JNI lib
export STLPORT_BASE=[NDK_stlport_location]
i.e: export STLPORT_BASE=/Users/bc/android-ndk-r8/sources/cxx-stl/stlport
ndk-build

Build project from cmd line
ant debug

Build project in Eclipse
Runs as -> Android Application

